text: Shanelle is a given name. Notable people with the name include: * Shanelle Arjoon (born 1997), Trinidadian footballer * Shanelle Jackson (born 1980), American politician * Shanelle Nyasiase (born 1997), Ethiopian-born South Sudanese fashion model. * Shanelle Porter (born 1972), American sprinter who specialized in the 400 metres * Shanelle Workman, American actress, voice actress, producer and director ==See also== * Chanelle, given name * Shonelle Jackson Category:Given names Category:Feminine given names Category:English- language feminine given names
title: Shanelle
